</ul>

<h3> Discoverability </h3>
<ul>
  <li> The comparison between both data sets is clear on the landing page and on the micro summaries </li>
  <li> Landing page maps are clickable and interacting with them will direct the user to the appropriate page </li>
</ul>

<h3> Simplicity </h3>
<ul>
  <li> Maps display large quantities of data in a compact and readable format </li>
  <li> Amount of text is limited with a greater focus places on maps and figures </li>
</ul>

<h3> Achievability </h3>
<ul>
  <li> D3's choropleth map makes making maps very achievable</li>
  <li> Other forms of charts and text are also intuitive to make</li>
</ul>

